OL,5, New paternity-leave rules come into    
OL,6, effect on Friday, for fathers in       
OL,7, England, Wales and Scotland.           
OL,9,FBut campaigners say they do not go far 
OL,10,Fenough and are calling on the          
OL,11,Fgovernment to give all new fathers more
OL,12,Ftime off at better pay.                
OL,14,FWhen Sean Craig was preparing for the  
OL,15,Farrival of his baby girl, he had hoped 
OL,16,Fto use two weeks' paternity leave to   
OL,17,Fspend time with his daughter.          
OL,19,FBut he and his partner, Bethany Lee,   
OL,20,Frealised they would not be able to     
OL,21,Fafford the "massive" drop in his wages.
